text: Elizabeth Joyce "Betty" Slade (18 June 1921 - 3 November 2000) was a British diver. She competed in the women's 3 metre springboard event at the 1936 Summer Olympics. ==References== ==External links== * * * Category:1921 births Category:2000 deaths Category:British female divers Category:Olympic divers of Great Britain Category:Divers at the 1936 Summer Olympics Category:Sportspeople from Leicester
